=== Best Function on Validation Set ===
Score: 5.6324% overhead

def priority(item: float, bins: np.ndarray) -> np.ndarray:
    return (item / (item + bins)) * (np.log(bins + 12) + np.exp(-(item - bins)**2 / (item + 5)) + np.sin(np.pi * (item - bins) / (item + 3)) + np.cos(2 * np.pi * (item - bins) / (item + 2)))

